{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-c5d3c097-c690-46e7-8dc7-df703ce57e0c-19\nfc_2ddc55cf-b79a-9cdc-9039-8dc2baa9d75c_4","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/细化修改8_需求.md","offset":85,"limit":50},"result":{"success":{"content":"### 2.0 角色全局化（路径 B 铁律）\n\n| 项 | 口径 |\n|----|------|\n| 角色真源 | **仅** `data/characters/<agentId>.json` + `/api/characters` |\n| 故事包不私有角色 | **禁止** `participants` 当白名单；作者不手维护 |\n| 「本包用到谁」 | `cards[].ownerAgentId` + effects 内 `agentId` + attach 目标归属 **派生** |\n| 编辑器锚点 | **全库**显示；挂卡数来自本包 cards；未用可灰显 |\n| 「添加角色」 | **仅**角色库新建；不是加入包 participants |\n| participants | 新包可不写；保存推荐不写；校验现场派生 |\n| layout.lanes | Studio 按库序或「有卡者优先」派生；引擎忽略 |\n\n### 2.1 引擎 validatePackage 改造\n\n1. **`collectReferencedAgentIds(bundle)`**：扫描 ownerAgentId、effects.agentId、end_story.next.agentId、attach 目标归属等（与 validate 一致）。\n2. **`REFERENCED_AGENT_UNKNOWN`**（error）：派生 id 不在角色库。\n3. **`validateParticipantsCharacters`** 对**派生集合**执行。\n4. **`PARTICIPANT_UNKNOWN`**：非空遗留 participants 未知 → **warning**「遗留字段将忽略」；空数组不报错。\n5. **ownerAgentId 不在旧 participants** 但在角色库 → 不得 error。\n\n### 2.2 包内卡生命周期（P0）\n\n| 操作 | 必须行为 |\n|------|----------|\n| 底栏放置新 CallCard | 生成 cardId；追加 `conf.cards[]`；新建 `cards/<cardId>.s-card.json`；画布节点与 conf 一致 |\n| 画布删除 CallCard | 从 `conf.cards[]` 移除；**删除**对应 s-card 文件（若 entryCardId 指向该卡则阻止或强制改入口） |\n| 保存整包 | `editorGraphToBundle` 写回 **conf.cards 与磁盘卡文件并集**（以画布为准），禁止只改 layout 不改 conf |\n| orphan 磁盘卡 | 未在 conf 索引的 s-card → validate `CARD_FILE_ORPHAN` warning；保存时可清理或保留策略写清 |\n\n**禁止：** 仅会话内新增节点，保存后 conf 仍只有打开时的卡列表。\n\n### 2.3 entryCardId 与 effect.critical\n\n| 项 | 口径 |\n|----|------|\n| entryCardId | 包配置或章节浮窗可 Select 本包 cardId；新建包默认指向首张 story 卡或占位 |\n| critical | 读盘保留；投影不丢；Effect 面板 boolean「失败则中止后续」；写回 effect.critical |\n\n### 2.4 ExitCondition 编辑器 v1（P0）\n\n**问题：** 现 `conditionSummary` 仅 UI 人话；写盘用 `base.condition ?? DEFAULT_CONDITION`，改 summary **不改**引擎 condition。\n\n**v1 必须：**\n\n| op | 面板 |\n|----|------|\n| `always` | 单选「始终」 |\n| `outcome_flag` | flag Select（对齐 OutcomeFlagSchema）+ equals 布尔 |\n| `beat_completed` | beatId Select（来自本卡 objectives.requiredBeats + 手填逃生） |\n| `beat_missing` | 同上 |","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":294,"fileSize":12906,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/细化修改8_需求.md","readRange":{"startLine":85,"endLine":134},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-c5d3c097-c690-46e7-8dc7-df703ce57e0c-19\nfc_2ddc55cf-b79a-9cdc-9039-8dc2baa9d75c_4","startedAtMs":"1784716616738","completedAtMs":"1784716616972"},"model_call_id":"e8f0e443-2f8a-4251-871d-51f79a3ac428-4-htaa","session_id":"eacc12ed-f499-44ba-b456-b70f5f1f7aa9","timestamp_ms":1784716617020}
{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-c5d3c097-c690-46e7-8dc7-df703ce57e0c-16\nfc_2ddc55cf-b79a-9cdc-9039-8dc2baa9d75c_1","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/packages/rpg-engine/tests/validation/wrong-number-act1.validate.test.ts"},"result":{"success":{"content":"/**\n * 模块名称：wrong_number_act1 validatePackage 回归（S8-3 · 路径 B 空 participants）\n */\nimport { cp, mkdtemp, rm } from \"node:fs/promises\";\nimport os from \"node:os\";\nimport path from \"node:path\";\nimport { fileURLToPath } from \"node:url\";\nimport { afterEach, describe, expect, it } from \"vitest\";\nimport { createEngineHost, hasBlockingErrors } from \"../../src/index.js\";\n\nconst repoRoot = path.resolve(\n  path.dirname(fileURLToPath(import.meta.url)),\n  \"../../../..\",\n);\nconst dataSrc = path.join(repoRoot, \"data\");\n\ndescribe(\"validatePackage wrong_number_act1 (S8-3)\", () => {\n  let tmpRoot: string | undefined;\n\n  afterEach(async () => {\n    if (tmpRoot) {\n      await rm(tmpRoot, { recursive: true, force: true });\n      tmpRoot = undefined;\n    }\n  });\n\n  it(\"has no blocking errors with omitted participants\", async () => {\n    tmpRoot = await mkdtemp(path.join(os.tmpdir(), \"airpc-val-wna-\"));\n    const dataRoot = path.join(tmpRoot, \"data\");\n    await cp(dataSrc, dataRoot, { recursive: true });\n\n    const host = createEngineHost({ persist: false, autoMemory: false });\n    await host.loadWorkspace(dataRoot);\n    const report = await host.validatePackage(\"wrong_number_act1\");\n    expect(hasBlockingErrors(report)).toBe(false);\n    expect(report.errors).toEqual([]);\n    expect(\n      report.warnings.some((e) => e.ruleId === \"PARTICIPANT_UNKNOWN\"),\n    ).toBe(false);\n  });\n});\n","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":42,"fileSize":1405,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/packages/rpg-engine/tests/validation/wrong-number-act1.validate.test.ts","readRange":{"startLine":1,"endLine":42},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-c5d3c097-c690-46e7-8dc7-df703ce57e0c-16\nfc_2ddc55cf-b79a-9cdc-9039-8dc2baa9d75c_1","startedAtMs":"1784716616731","completedAtMs":"1784716616974"},"model_call_id":"e8f0e443-2f8a-4251-871d-51f79a3ac428-4-htaa","session_id":"eacc12ed-f499-44ba-b456-b70f5f1f7aa9","timestamp_ms":1784716617021}
